Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal — Public Domain Dedication

This repository collects open-source game assets. Each subdirectory contains
assets under their respective licenses — see subdirectory LICENSE files for
specific terms.

The curation code, tooling, and original contents of this repository (other
than the included third-party assets) are dedicated to the public domain under
CC0 1.0 by sigco3111.

Third-party assets retain their original licenses:
  free/            — Various CC0/CC-BY/MIT (see per-asset LICENSE files)
  curated/         — Re-distribution of metadata links; original data retains owner licenses
  extracted/       — Assets extracted from open-source games under their original licenses
                     (e.g., Battle for Wesnoth = CC-BY for assets, GPL-2.0 for code)

For commercial use of any asset: verify its subdirectory LICENSE file before deployment.
